{"tid":440830,"cid":34,"subCid":0,"title":"(台測)巨影都市","createTime":"2017-10-19T06:24:17.000Z","updateTime":"2017-10-20T10:34:26.000Z","uid":29160,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"86af019111de53bf8ac9f32f4c0164b99975ebcc","tid":440830,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-19T06:24:17.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">玩唔曬下次播返</span><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.twitch.tv/thanksyour\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.twitch.tv%2Fthanksyour&d=PtFwCEnN4a7PJ%2F0UQYE76NU7RO4jIL0fLOArxO5LqtQ%3D&h=92de1ff9\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.twitch.tv/thanksyour</a><br />\n<img src=\"https://p2.bahamut.com.tw/M/2KU/88/0001589488.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fp2.bahamut.com.tw%2FM%2F2KU%2F88%2F0001589488.JPG&h=9d36b855&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n《巨影都市》（日語：巨影都市）是Granzella開發並由萬代南夢宮娛樂發行在PlayStation 4平台上的生存類動作冒險遊戲。遊戲是《絕體絕命都市》系列製作人九條一馬離開Irem成立Granzella後的第一款遊戲，故本作也被看作是《絕體絕命都市》的精神續作。[1]在遊戲中，玩家需要從各個著名的特設和科幻作品中的怪獸、巨型機器人等戰鬥場景中全力脫身逃命。而藉助萬代南夢宮的IP版權，像《奧特曼》、《哥吉拉》、《機動警察》、《新世紀福音戰士》的作品中的知名戰鬥場景都能在遊戲中體現<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://addons.mozilla.org/en-US/firefox/addon/ghostery/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Faddons.mozilla.org%2Fen-US%2Ffirefox%2Faddon%2Fghostery%2F&d=PtFwCEnN4a7PJ%2F0UQYE76NU7RO4jIL0fLOArxO5LqtQ%3D&h=c9e6801a\" target=\"_blank\">https://addons.mozilla.org/en-US/firefox/addon/ghostery/</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://chrome.google.com/webstore/detail/ghostery/mlomiejdfkolichcflejclcbmpeaniij?hl=zh-TW\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fchrome.google.com%2Fwebstore%2Fdetail%2Fghostery%2Fmlomiejdfkolichcflejclcbmpeaniij%3Fhl%3Dzh-TW&d=PtFwCEnN4a7PJ%2F0UQYE76NU7RO4jIL0fLOArxO5LqtQ%3D&h=7fdffaa7\" target=\"_blank\">https://chrome.google.com/webstore/detail/ghostery/mlomiejdfkolichcflejclcbmpeaniij?hl=zh-TW</a><br />\n裝左睇V台就唔會見左上果舊野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid